org.gitlab.api

Class GitlabProject

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gitlab.api.GitlabProject

  • public final class GitlabProject
extends java.lang.Object
    This class serves as instance of Gitlab component Project. To create, update, or delete this issue, call create(), update(), or delete() explicitly. This supports query for projects globally that are visible by current user or projects owned by a specific user. See GitlabProject.Query and GitlabProject.UserQuery.

    Gitlab Web API: https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/api/projects.html
